      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Two-letter words are the secret weapons of competitive Scrabble. They don't just fill gaps — with the right premium square placement, a single two-letter play can score more than many five-letter words. Here's how to maximise points from minimal tiles.</p>

