      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Parallel Play Multiplier</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300">The real power of 2-letter words comes from parallel plays — placing your word alongside an existing word so you form multiple valid 2-letter combinations simultaneously:</p>

