          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Target DWS/TWS for the main word:</span> Place your 2-letter word so the entire word lands on a Double or Triple Word Score. The cross-words don't get multiplied, but the main word does — ZA on TWS = 33 base + cross-word points.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
